[575.377852, "o", "    47\t            int lo = hexval(in[i+2]);\r\n    48\t            if (hi < 0 || lo < 0) return -1;\r\n    49\t            out[oi++] = (char)((hi << 4) | lo);\r\n    50\t            i += 2;\r\n    51\t        } else {\r\n    52\t            out[oi++] = in[i];\r\n    53\t        }\r\n    54\t    }\r\n"]
